            "title": "稅貸｜借低息稅貸 造高息定存 三個情景拆解 賺唔賺到息差？",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"借稅貸 造定存｜銀行稅貸優惠又出動，低息稅貸吸引大家借錢交稅，或貸款以迎合其他財務需要，例如就有人想到，趁現時不少銀行定期存款利率仍然吸引，只要稅貸利率低過定期存款利率，大可借稅貸造定存「賺息差」，實現「錢搵錢」。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WLKEDuxDiXERTLtgA3xy7g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/edaab710-c6af-11f0-9fde-822ab291e7ba\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">借稅貸 造定存｜銀行稅貸優惠又出動，低息稅貸吸引大家借錢交稅，或貸款以迎合其他財務需要，例如就有人想到，趁現時不少銀行定期存款利率仍然吸引，只要稅貸利率低過定期存款利率，大可借稅貸造定存「賺息差」，實現「錢搵錢」。</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">借稅貸 造定存｜銀行稅貸優惠又出動，低息稅貸吸引大家借錢交稅，或貸款以迎合其他財務需要，例如就有人想到，趁現時不少銀行定期存款利率仍然吸引，只要稅貸利率低過定期存款利率，大可借稅貸造定存「賺息差」，實現「錢搵錢」。今文就用三個情境案例，和大家拆解一下！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">以下三個情境，帶出三個重點：</p><ol class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>借得愈少，水位愈少</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>小心減息，得不償失</strong></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-decimal\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>魔鬼細節，必須清楚</strong></p></li></ol><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>🤹🏻 情境一：完美情境－－借150萬賺33,452元</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">假設向<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:恒生稅貸1;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=$%7BGDPR%7D;gdpr_consent=$%7BGDPR_CONSENT_755%7D;ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">恒生稅貸1</a>50萬元，還款期12個月，實際年息率為1.68厘，總利息支出為13,590元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2236be80-31c8-4bee-9ffc-79b162ce92d3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然後利用這150萬元，到富邦銀行享用「Fubon+ 手機應用程式限定 ─ 特優港元定期存款優惠」敍造3個月3.1厘定期存款，到期後本金連利息再敍造3個月定期，如此類推，做滿4期共12個月。假設每期「完美地」均同樣找到3個月3.1厘息，四期分別收到利息11,625元、11,715元、11,805元、11,897元，合計收息總共47,042元。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">完美情境的結果，就是透過稅貸150萬元，12個月後賺得33,452元。不過，這個「完美情境」需要多方配合，包括：貸款人月薪需達62,500元或以上才合資格貸款150萬元（恒生最高可貸款月薪24倍）、貸款人需有充裕資金每月準時償還126,132.5元稅貸欠款、每期做定存都找到3個月3.1厘或以上的息率等等。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1545\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e4vPEGw74EmCNHju.AHTTA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTE1NDU-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/d35175c0-c6a5-11f0-bf3d-8fc895fb9e47\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=$%7BGDPR%7D;gdpr_consent=$%7BGDPR_CONSENT_755%7D;ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"恒生銀行稅貸150萬元，實際年利率1.68%。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"773\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/soqr2ugp7_nqqHsi9aPLVA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc3Mw--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/2feedf20-c6a6-11f0-baff-77a138468118\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:恒生銀行稅貸;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=${GDPR};gdpr_consent=${GDPR_CONSENT_755};ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">恒生銀行稅貸</a>150萬元，實際年利率1.68%。</figcaption></div></a><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=$%7BGDPR%7D;gdpr_consent=$%7BGDPR_CONSENT_755%7D;ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"恒生銀行稅貸150萬元，還款期12個月，每月還款126,132.5元。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"889\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/bH.seM3_K_M_pYwVjhajkQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg4OQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/2fef2d41-c6a6-11f0-bbfc-14b8c8413a34\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:恒生銀行;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=${GDPR};gdpr_consent=${GDPR_CONSENT_755};ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">恒生銀行</a>稅貸150萬元，還款期12個月，每月還款126,132.5元。</figcaption></div></a><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>🤹🏻 情境二：如果減息 會帶來咩影響？</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">為方便比較，稅貸部分與上述的情境一相同，貸款150萬元，總利息支出同為13,590元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然後同樣利用這150萬元，到富邦銀行享用「Fubon+ 手機應用程式限定 ─ 特優港元定期存款優惠」敍造3個月3.1厘定期存款，到期後本金連利息再敍造3個月定期，如此類推，做滿4期共12個月。假設到第三期及第四期時，由於減息因素，只能找到2.5厘息，則四期分別收到利息11,625元、11,715元、9,250元、9,578元，合計總共42,168元。計及總利息支出13,590元，即12個月後賺得28,578元（上述的情境一為33,452元）。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">減息的結果，就是賺取金額明顯減少，這個金額只是因應情境的假設而定，定存減息的幅度有可能與上述假設有所不同。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1324\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/n8JJcwAXksu_tKmUTrFUJw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEzMjQ-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/d36a54f0-c6a5-11f0-bcfb-6e92d7291287\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>🤹🏻 情境三：月薪3萬借盡24倍＋如果減息</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">月薪3萬元想借盡稅貸，暫時以<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:恒生;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=$%7BGDPR%7D;gdpr_consent=$%7BGDPR_CONSENT_755%7D;ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">恒生</a>24倍月薪為最高，借盡可貸款72萬元，還款期為12個月，實際年息率為3.81厘，總利息支出為14,688元。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">然後利用這72萬元，到富邦銀行享用「Fubon+ 手機應用程式限定 ─ 特優港元定期存款優惠」敍造3個月3.1厘定期存款，到期後本金連利息再敍造3個月定期，如此類推，做滿4期共12個月。假設到第三期及第四期時，由於減息因素，只能找到2.5厘息，則四期分別收到利息5,580元、5,623元、4,570元、4,598元，合計總共20,371元。計及總利息支出14,688元，即12個月後賺得5,683元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"1247\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/sZ4V_KH1Hu9ZjEhEh8Mqfg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTEyNDc-/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/d3390bc0-c6a5-11f0-9f4b-48945767c1fd\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=$%7BGDPR%7D;gdpr_consent=$%7BGDPR_CONSENT_755%7D;ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"恒生銀行稅貸150萬元，實際年利率3.81%。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"759\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/HHm4j3PT09XnVVZxMrNjEg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTc1OQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/2fef2d40-c6a6-11f0-bce7-ff9777bfc0f0\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:恒生銀行稅貸;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=${GDPR};gdpr_consent=${GDPR_CONSENT_755};ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">恒生銀行稅貸</a>150萬元，實際年利率3.81%。</figcaption></div></a><a class=\"mb-module-gap\" data-ylk=\"elm:img;elmt:link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=$%7BGDPR%7D;gdpr_consent=$%7BGDPR_CONSENT_755%7D;ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"恒生銀行稅貸72萬元，還款期12個月，每月還款61,224元。\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"870\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lqPlM1I6ZLaMykIW5QlpPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTg3MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-11/2feeb810-c6a6-11f0-ad7f-5b1b05a2fac5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:恒生銀行稅貸;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://ad.doubleclick.net/ddm/trackclk/N1402310.160910YAHOOFINANCE/B34358401.432251103;dc_trk_aid=624798428;dc_trk_cid=244052235;dc_lat=;dc_rdid=;tag_for_child_directed_treatment=;tfua=;gdpr=${GDPR};gdpr_consent=${GDPR_CONSENT_755};ltd=;dc_tdv=1\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">恒生銀行稅貸</a>72萬元，還款期12個月，每月還款61,224元。</figcaption></div></a><h2 class=\"mb-module-gap leading-[1.35] text-px22 font-bold lg:text-px24 text-batcave\"><strong>🤹🏻 結論：貸款金額要夠大 才具值博空間 但月薪又要有返咁上下才借到</strong></h2><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">由上述三個情境可見，貸款額愈低，實際年息率就會愈高，利息支出也反而更大；轉過來看，存款額愈低，定期息率也較低，定存收取利息的金額也減少，結果可賺取的金額也大幅降低。倘若往後定存息率大幅調低，這種「套息」交易更有可能得不償失！</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>延伸閱讀：</strong></p><ul class=\"mb-module-gap\"><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:稅貸2025｜最平稅貸利息、現金優惠回贈大比拼 抓緊借平錢機會｜Yahoo財經;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E7%A8%85%E8%B2%B8-%E4%BD%8E%E6%81%AF-%E6%9C%80%E5%B9%B3-%E5%88%A9%E6%81%AF-%E7%A8%85%E5%8B%99%E8%B2%B8%E6%AC%BE-%E5%80%9F%E5%B9%B3%E9%8C%A2-%E5%AF%A6%E9%9A%9B%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87-apr-%E7%8F%BE%E9%87%91-%E5%9B%9E%E8%B4%88-%E5%84%AA%E6%83%A0-%E9%82%84%E6%AC%BE%E6%9C%9F-084016130.html\"><strong>稅貸2025｜最平稅貸利息、現金優惠回贈大比拼 抓緊借平錢機會｜Yahoo財經</strong></a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:借低息稅貸 造高息定存 魔鬼細節要留意！｜Yahoo財經;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;outcm:mb_qualified_link;_E:mb_qualified_link;ct:story;\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E4%BD%8E%E6%81%AF-%E7%A8%85%E8%B2%B8-%E9%AB%98%E6%81%AF-%E5%AE%9A%E6%9C%9F-%E5%AD%98%E6%AC%BE-%E5%A5%97%E6%81%AF-%E9%AD%94%E9%AC%BC-%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE-%E7%B4%B0%E7%AF%80-%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF-130532510.html\"><strong>借低息稅貸 造高息定存 魔鬼細節要留意！｜Yahoo財經</strong></a></p></li><li class=\"ml-4 list-disc\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link yahoo-link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1